ovie || Czech\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\" | '''[[Portuguese language|Portuguese]]''' ||  Isto para mim \u00e9 chin\u00eas. || {{IPA-pt|\u02c8i\u0283tu p\u0259\u027e\u0259 \u02c8m\u0129 \u025b \u0283i\u02c8ne\u0283|}} || This is Chinese to me || Chinese <small>(Portugal)</small>\n|-\n| Isto para mim \u00e9 grego. ||{{IPA-pt|\u02c8i\u0283tu p\u0259\u027e\u0259 \u02c8m\u0129 \u025b \u02c8\u0263\u027ee\u0263u|}} || This is Greek to me || Greek <small>(Portugal)</small>\n|-\n| N\u00e3o entendo grego/hebraico/aramaico. || {{IPA|[n\u025c\u0303w \u0129\u02c8t\u1ebddu \u02c8\u0261\u027ee\u0263u]|}}, {{IPA|[\u0129\u02c8t\u1ebdd e\u02c8b\u027eajku]|}}, {{IPA|[\u0129\u02c8t\u1ebdd(w) \u025c\u027e\u0259\u02c8majku]|}} || I don't understand Greek/Hebrew/Aramaic || Greek, Hebrew, Aramaic <small>(Brazil)</small>\n|-\n| N\u00e3o falo grego/hebraico/aramaico. ||{{IPA|[n\u025c\u0303w \u02c8falu \u02c8\u0261\u027ee\u0263u]|}}, {{IPA|[\u02c8fal e\u02c8b\u027eajku]|}}, {{IPA|\u02c8[fal(w) \u025c\u027e\u0259\u02c8majku]|}} || I don't speak Greek/Hebrew/Aramaic || Greek, Hebrew, Aramaic <small>(Brazil)</small>\n|-\n| Voc\u00ea est\u00e1 falando grego/latim/\u00e1rabe.<br>Voc\u00ea fala em... <small>''(ditto)''</small> ||{{IPA|[\u02c8se \u02c8ta f\u025c\u02c8l\u025c\u0303du \u02c8\u0261\u027ee\u0263u]|}}, {{IPA|[l\u0250\u02c8t\u0283\u0129]|}}, {{IPA|[\u02c8a\u027e\u0259\u03b2i]|}}<br>{{IPA|[vo\u02c8se \u02c8fal\u0259\u032f \u0129 \u02c8\u0261\u027ee\u0263u|}} (...)] || You are speaking Greek/Latin/Arabic. || Greek, Latin, Arabic <small>(Brazil)</small>\n|-\n| Voc\u00ea est\u00e1 falando grego/latim/\u00e1rabe? ||{{IPA|[\u02c8se \u02c8ta f\u025c\u02c8l\u025c\u0303du \u02c8\u0261\u027ee\u0263u|}} (...)] || Are you speaking Greek/Latin/Arabic? || Greek, Latin, Arabic <small>(Brazil)</small>\n|-\n| N\u00e3o leio japon\u00eas.<br>N\u00e3o sei ler japon\u00eas/\u00e1rabe. ||{{IPA|[n\u025c\u0303w \u02c8lej.ju \u0292\u025cpu\u02c8ne\u0283]|}}<br>{{IPA|[n\u025c\u0303w \u02c8sej \u02c8le\u0281 \u0292\u0250p